      <title>欧盟将对中国电动汽车征收最高 45% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧盟周五投票决定对来自中国的电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税，此举将加剧与北京的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果就业数据符合预期，美国银行的 Hartnett 认为风险偏好将上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/bofa-s-hartnett-sees-risk-on-rally-if-jobs-data-is-as-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师迈克尔哈特内特表示，如果周五公布的美国月度就业报告符合预期，风险资产就有可能上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/bofa-s-hartnett-sees-risk-on-rally-if-jobs-data-is-as-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国建筑业在预算前大幅增长，为 Starmer 助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/uk-construction-sector-surges-in-pre-budget-boost-for-starmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项重要调查显示，9 月份英国建筑业以两年半以来的最快速度增长，在经历了数周的经济负面情绪之后，这对首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 来说是一个提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/uk-construction-sector-surges-in-pre-budget-boost-for-starmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
