      <title>景顺中国首席投资官预测股市上涨 但对估值感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/invesco-china-cio-who-called-rally-is-worried-about-valuations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[景顺投资有限公司 (Invesco Ltd.) 香港和中国大陆首席投资官马雷蒙德 (Raymond Ma) 曾预测今年中国股市将实现两位数的回报，他表示，有迹象表明部分股票的涨幅过大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/invesco-china-cio-who-called-rally-is-worried-about-valuations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 04:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
