      <title>股市上涨刺激需求，人人都想购买港元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hong-kong-dollar-in-rare-spotlight-as-stock-rally-boosts-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着在香港交易所上市的中国股票大幅上涨，需求飙升，长期处于休眠状态的香港货币开始苏醒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hong-kong-dollar-in-rare-spotlight-as-stock-rally-boosts-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 03:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
